---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Coolify Cloud"
  canonicalUrl="https://coolify.io/cloud/"
  description="Coolify Cloud offers managed hosting with high availability, free emails, and priority support. Same price, more benefits."
>
  <h1
    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl px-4"
  >
    Why use Coolify Cloud<span class="text-warning">?</span>
  </h1>
  <h2 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    Self-hosting and Cloud... What?
  </h2>
  <div class="pb-2 flex justify-center text-center gap-8 px-4">
    <a
      href="https://app.coolify.io/register"
      class="text-base font-bold rounded p-4 px-10 text-white bg-coolgray-300 hover:bg-coolgray-400 flex gap-2 w-64 justify-center"
      ><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 15 15" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path
          fill="currentColor"
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="m6.854 3.854l.8-.8c.644-.645 1.775-1.092 2.898-1.253a5.342 5.342 0 0 1 1.504-.02c.443.066.714.196.84.323c.127.126.257.397.323.84c.064.427.059.95-.02 1.504c-.16 1.123-.608 2.254-1.253 2.898L7.5 11.793l-1.146-1.146a.5.5 0 1 0-.708.707l1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .708 0l.547-.548l1.17 1.951a.5.5 0 0 0 .783.097l2-2a.5.5 0 0 0 .141-.425l-.465-3.252l.624-.623c.855-.856 1.358-2.225 1.535-3.465c.09-.627.1-1.25.019-1.794c-.08-.528-.256-1.05-.604-1.399c-.349-.348-.871-.525-1.4-.604a6.333 6.333 0 0 0-1.793.02C9.17.987 7.8 1.49 6.946 2.345l-.623.624l-3.252-.465a.5.5 0 0 0-.425.141l-2 2a.5.5 0 0 0 .097.783l1.95 1.17l-.547.547a.5.5 0 0 0 0 .708l1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 1 0 .708-.708L3.207 7.5l.647-.646zm3.245 9.34l-.97-1.617l2.017-2.016l.324 2.262zM3.423 5.87l2.016-2.016l-2.262-.324l-1.37 1.37zm-1.07 4.484a.5.5 0 1 0-.707-.708l-1 1a.5.5 0 1 0 .708.707zm1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 1 0-.707-.707l-2 2a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.707zm1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 1 0-.707-.708l-1 1a.5.5 0 1 0 .708.707zM9.5 6.749a1.249 1.249 0 1 0 0-2.498a1.249 1.249 0 0 0 0 2.498"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
      </svg>Get Started</a
    >
    <a
      href="/pricing"
      class="text-base font-bold rounded p-4 px-10 text-white bg-coolgray-300 hover:bg-coolgray-400 flex gap-2 w-64 justify-center"
      ><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <g
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path d="M15 11v.01M5.173 8.378a3 3 0 1 1 4.656-1.377"></path>
          <path
            d="M16 4v3.803A6.019 6.019 0 0 1 18.658 11h1.341a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1.342c-.336.95-.907 1.8-1.658 2.473V19.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0v-.583a6.04 6.04 0 0 1-1 .083h-4a6.04 6.04 0 0 1-1-.083v.583a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0v-2.027A6 6 0 0 1 8.999 7h2.5z"
          ></path>
        </g>
      </svg>Pricing</a
    >
  </div>
  <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-2">
    <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-neutral-400  text-left">
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning"
            >Same Price, More Benefits.</strong
          > Self-hosting requires one server for Coolify and at least one more for your deployments, as recommended. Each server costs around $5 per month. With Cloud hosting, you can get Coolify for the same price, but with additional benefits.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Highly Available.</strong>
          The Cloud instance is designed to be highly available and always prepared to handle your requests, eliminating the need for you to manage it.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Free Emails.</strong> Email notifications are included in the cost and there is no requirement to pay for a third-party provider.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Less Maintenance.</strong> You are not required to manage your Coolify instance. We handle it for you.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Priority Support.</strong>
          We are available to assist you whenever you require support via Email or Chat.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <svg
          class="mt-0 h-6 w-6 flex-none text-warning"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Brag About It.</strong> 
          You can impress anyone by saying that you self-host in the Cloud. They will definitely be amazed.
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
